Divided Sky player help
bank

.SH Name
.SI 5
bank - a place to hold all your money in
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
balance
open account
close account
deposit <money>
withdraw <money>
draw bond for <money>
draw bond for <money> from account
cash in <bond>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to store money in a safe place, some of the banks have
multiple branches open in different areas of the land.
Some banks also provide the possibility to draw and cash in money bonds.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> open account
> close account
> deposit 12 gold coins, 4 platinum coins
> withdraw 5 gold coins, 4 platinum coins
> draw bond for 10 gold coins, 2 electrum coins
> draw bond for 10 gold coins, 2 electrum coins from account
> cash in bonds
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
None
.EP